			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=wizardbalance&message.id=2570#M2570">75</a> of 234
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 308 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV><BR>
<DIV>Guys, some of you are very good at working out the mathematical calculations here. I was reading some of the other threads and came across the following post in the Necromancer forum.&nbsp;Any thoughts on the wizard figures below? 161 mana regen a tick? Sustained ("24/7") dps of 256 using CoV?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>
<HR>
</DIV>
<DIV>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>Necros need more mana, consider the following:<BR><BR>Typical group,<BR>SK (pretty much the only tanks who hold aggro well)<BR>Bst (slower and DPS)<BR>Bard (the only pullers that can pull zones like RSS)<BR>cleric (well seriously)<BR>(necro) only because I'm only in groups I'm in.<BR>random...<BR><BR>SK hp/mana tap<BR>Bst crack<BR>Bard mana<BR>cleric<BR>Necro MW<BR>random dps<BR><BR>Assuming we get a wizzie for the last slot.<BR>SK13<BR>BST10<BR>BRD22<BR>CLRnil (boxed chanter) 20<BR>NEC30 (costs us 30 too)<BR>random dps<BR>FT20 +3 from AA<BR>2 from FS<BR>4 mana a tick from familiar<BR>A wiz in the last spot will get 124 mana a tick standing<BR>assume 16 mana a tick from clickies<BR>(maelins methodical mind + Aura of Taelosia or any other combination.)<BR>140 mana a tick total<BR>outdoor zones add 21 a tick from drog<BR>161 a tick<BR><BR>A necro in the same group, spending 30 mana a tick on MW...<BR>SK13<BR>BST10<BR>BRD22<BR>CLRnil 0 from C6<BR>NEc-30 + 50 from SoS (no I do not have dark possession)<BR>random dps<BR>FT20 +3 from AA<BR>2 from FS<BR>A necro will get 90 mana a tick standing<BR>assume 16 mana a tick from clickies<BR>(maelins methodical mind + Aura of Taelosia or any other combination.)<BR>106 mana a tick total<BR>drog useless having to FD to wipe aggro.<BR>106 a tick<BR><BR>Wizzie regens it 55 mana a tick faster than me.<BR><BR>Claw of Vox<BR>1375 dmg<BR>208 mana<BR>-------<BR>6.61 dmg per mana,<BR>Cast (5) + Recast = (2.25) = 7.25 seconds<BR><BR>In a 60 second fight can be cast 8 times<BR>11000 dmg done<BR><BR>183 dps, 1664 mana used<BR>Count 40% chance to crit<BR>15400 dmg done,<BR>256 dps<BR><BR>During that 1 min fight, he regened 1400 mana<BR>12 seconds later he is again, at FM.<BR><BR>Count Mana Pres items and foci and he can chain cast CoV 24/7 doing more damage than before.<BR><BR>Sustained 256 dps.<BR>-------------------------------<BR><BR>Necro<BR>MW (only spell that will land this early without debuffs) 300<BR>DDarkness (200 mana x 2 to land it) 400 (used as a test to see if mob is tashed yet cant land snare cant land zilch)<BR>DN 585 x 2 (casting FoD x 2 is way to wasteful to use, have to get DN on early)<BR>FoD 750<BR>mana used 2890<BR><BR>mob is inc, pet attack<BR>at 6 seconds MW lands<BR>at 8.25 spell gems refresh<BR>at 11.45 darkness 1 fails<BR>FD between gem refreshes<BR>at 13.70 gems refresh<BR>at 16.90 snare lands<BR>FD between gem refreshes<BR>at 19.15 spell gems refresh<BR>at 24.65 DN lands<BR>FD between gem refreshes<BR>at 26.9 gems refresh<BR>at 32.9 FoD lands<BR>FD<BR><BR><BR>Manawise can only afford to Recast one spell DN at 20% to 30% of mobs health if fight lasts longer <BR>(avgs out to 98.5 dps at this point if recast as it fades,but horribly inefficient)<BR><BR>In a 60 second fight.<BR>assuming dots begin doing dmg instantly(they dont)<BR>Darkness was on for (60-16.9 seconds doing 96 a tick)= ((60-16.9)/10) x 96 = 413.76<BR>DN ((60-24.65)/10) * 591 = 2089.19<BR>FoD ((60-32.9)/10) * 370 = 1002.7<BR><BR>= 3505.65 dmg<BR><BR>= 58.43 dps.<BR><BR>+ 47 dps from pet<BR>= 105.42 dps<BR><BR>with dot crits maxed,<BR>69.07<BR>+ 47 from pet<BR>116.07 dps<BR><BR>for a mana cost of 2305<BR>--<BR><BR>in a 90 second fight<BR>add 30 seconds of DN working<BR>591 x 5 = 2955<BR>30 seconds of DDarkness<BR>96 x 5 = 480<BR>2 ticks of FoD (lasts the fight now)<BR>370 x 2 = 740<BR>for an additional 4175 dmg<BR><BR>7680.65 over 90 seconds<BR>85.34 dps<BR>+47 from pet = 132.34 dps<BR><BR>dot crits maxed<BR>100.7 dps<BR>+47 from pet = 147.7 dps<BR><BR>2890 mana used<BR><BR>2890 mana will take me 27.5 ticks to regenerate, 15 ticks went by. Must sit and med for 90 seconds before next mob.<BR><BR>On the longer fight damage per mana = 2.66<BR><BR>keep in mind dark nightmare is constantly resisted!<BR><BR>2.66 dmg per mana after crit AAs, vs 11.3 dmg per mana for the wizzie with nuke AAs maxed (225% dmg crits x 1.25 AA familiar! x 1.25 Advanced FOMM)<BR>Say we both get a focus like Muram's Vengeance<BR>3.74 DPM vs 15.82<BR><BR>So, where... exactly is the balance?</P>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE></DIV>
<DIV>
